== Description == <!--T:3-->

<!--T:4-->
The [[Image:BIM_Shape2DCut.svg|24px]] [[BIM_Shape2DCut|BIM Shape2DCut]] tool inherits from [[Image:BIM_Shape2DView.svg|24px]] [[BIM_Shape2DView|BIM Shape2DView]]. It performs the same initial action but then sets the resulting object's `ProjectionMode` to `"Cutfaces"`. This means the final 2D object will only display the geometry that is directly intersected by the section plane, creating a true "section cut" view.

